description: The strong and powerful Gymnast (Ranked 8th) got her first win and now looks forward to advancing up the US ladder. She comes in to this match even stronger, and feels confident that the Goddess will go down. The Goddess (ranked 5th) has only lost one match this season, and is looking to repeat the lightweight Championship. The Gymnast is in her way and The Goddess will not let that stop her.
title: The Gymnast (1-2) The Goddess (8-4)
